snippet.title: Lloyd the Monkey - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
...Yeah, we're jumping the gun a bit on this, but Lloyd the Monkey launches next Saturday, so why wouldn't we want to share this? Be there at the Sonic Amateur Games Expo or at lloydthemonkey.com or even on Kongregate to begin our simian hero's adventures all over again on September 30th!

Music - One OK Rock (Ketsuraku Automation)
